I'm a data analyst, experiment designer, and budding programmer. This is my GitHub site.

I did most of the work for Coursera's [R Programming](  https://www.coursera.org/course/rprog) and [Getting and Cleaning Data](https://www.coursera.org/course/getdata) courses.
